specific_model: CHRONOFIGHTER SUPERLIGHT CARBON SKELETON - TRANSLUCENT ORANGE
nickname: CHRONOFIGHTER SUPERLIGHT CARBON SKELETON - TRANSLUCENT ORANGE
description:
As part of Graham's 25th anniversary celebrations, the company produced a recreation of its inaugural watch, first released in 1995. 

The Chronofighter Vintage 25th anniversary features a bi-compax dial configuration. The silver toned counters are snailed and stand out from the main black dial. The overall composition exhibits symmetry and delivers peerless readability.
